title: Horn Ok Please - Food Stall
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Indian, Fast food, Take-out only
description: Indian food stall at the Southbank Food Market, Borough Market, and other venues - check its webpage for dates & times. Food is vegan except for optional yoghurt sauce. Choice of 3 mains; samosa topped with chickpeas, chutneys and pomegranate; puffed rice;  crispy noodle and vegetable dish; and spiced lentil crepe.
streetAddress: The Real Food Market, Kings Cross Square, Euston Rd
